standard  of  100  megabits  per  second  in  both  directions  because 
uploading matters as well. Otherwise, we are only receiving, we are 
not sharing. And his resolution would call for 100 megabits per sec-
ond  by  2015.  We  need  goals  like  this  and  we  need  the  action  to 
