this morning because of the 4 hour time zone difference. 

I want to show you first—this is a chart that shows the road map 
of  the  United  States,  the  roads  in  the  South  48  and  the  roads  in 
Alaska.  Now,  in  Alaska,  without  roads,  we  proceeded  to  adopt  the 
whole  concept  of  telemedicine,  and  the  YKHC,  headed  by  Gene 
Peltola, has led in this effort. 

