people  realize  how  much  low-income  housing  there  is  in  rural 
America. I am certainly aware of that. 

Let  me  correct  the  record.  I  do  not  think  $22  million  is  a  paltry 
amount of money. It is compared to the Missouri budget of $20 bil-
lion.  So  $22  million  is  not  enough  out  of  a  budget  of  $20  billion  to 
go toward this from the State level. 

So thank you. 
Senator STEVENS. Will the Senator yield there, though? 
Senator MCCASKILL. Yes. 
